title: Tik Tok fame Athulya Palakkal confirms her marriage to Tamil actor Dhileepan Pugazhendi
summary: Athulya and Dhileepan got married on May 4. The couple have been together for 28 years. Athulya is a popular actress in the Tamil film industry. She is best known for her role in the film ‘Yeven’ and has appeared in other films.

title: ‘Hyderabad is lucky for me’, Aman Gupta of Shark Tank India fame- The New Indian Express
summary: Aman Gupta is Co Founder & CMO at boAt, an audio & wearables brand. “Harvard Business School invited me. It calls me every year. It wrote a case study on us, but ISB ignored me. Looks like Indian business schools don’t value their own people,” said Gupta.
